This is the '''discography''' of American singer '''[[Iggy Pop]]'''. The following lists of all of Pop's released [[Single (music)|singles]], [[studio album]]s, [[compilation album]]s, [[Extended play|EPs]], [[Demo (music)|demos]] and [[videography]].

''For a detailed listing of Iggy Pop's albums and singles with The Stooges, see: [[The Stooges discography|The Stooges Discography]].''

==Albums==
* All releases are credited to Iggy Pop as solo works unless stated otherwise.
