==Contributions==
* ''[[Low (David Bowie album)|Low]]'' (1977, RCA) - "[[What in the World]]" (with [[David Bowie]])
* ''[[Tonight (David Bowie album)|Tonight]]'' (1984, EMI America) - "[[Dancing with the Big Boys]]" (with [[David Bowie]])
* ''[[Repo Man (film)|Repo Man]]'' (1984, MCA) - Title track from film
* ''[[Red Hot + Blue]]'' (1990, Chrysalis) - "[[Well, Did You Evah!]]" (with [[Deborah Harry]])
* ''[[Arizona Dream (soundtrack)|Arizona Dream]]'' (1993, Mercury) - "In the Deathcar", "TV Screen", "Get the Money", "This is a Film" (with [[Goran Bregović]])
* ''[[Système D]]'' (1993, Virgin Records) - "My Love Is Bad" (with [[Les Rita Mitsouko]])
* ''[[Space Goofs]]'' (1997) - "Monster Men"
* ''[[The Contino Sessions]]'' (1999, Concrete) - "Aisha" (with [[Death in Vegas]])
* ''[[Fatherfucker]]'' (2003, Beggars XL) - "[[Kick It]]" (with [[Peaches (musician)|Peaches]])
* ''[[Dark Night of the Soul (album)|Dark Night of the Soul]] (2010) - "Pain" (with [[Danger Mouse]] & [[Sparklehorse]])
* '' Black Sunshine (With [[Rob Zombie]])
* ''[[Relationship of Command]]'' - "[[Rolodex Propaganda]]" (with At The Drive-In)
* ''[[Profanation (Preparation for a Coming Darkness)]]'' - "Furies"
* ''[[Slash (album)|Slash]]'' (2010, EMI/Roadrunner) - "We're All Gonna Die" (with [[Slash (musician)|Slash]])
*''[[From Gainsbourg to Lulu]]'' (2011) - "Initials BB " (with [[Lulu Gainsbourg]])

